NAGIOS

1. docker pull jasonrivers/nagios:latest
2. docker run --name nagiosdemo -p 8888:80 jasonrivers/nagios:latest

OPEN http://localhost:8888

Login:
username: nagiosadmin
password: nagios

3. docker stop nagiosdemo


